Later when it was time to leave since we did not feel the need to stay, the bill was rang up incorrectly.
I did not understand how we got happy hour prices on the food but not the drinks..Well luckily one of the managers or at least the men in suits were around because of course the waiter was missing.
They corrected the order and we got the right bill...And that explains the zero tip left to our waiter.
Overall the resturant was nice, the decor was awesome, and maybe we just got the raw end of the deal on the section that we sat in...But thats why I gave the two stars.

