It looks like something they might pour your water with in a restaurant in Mexico maybe?
So it gets poured into these tiny little glasses.
The water is warm and is clearly tap water.
I'm perfectly fine with tap water at restaurants.
Next time, just fill a glass up with ice and turn on the sink.
At least it will be cold, which usually helps to mask the tap flavor.
Get rid of this lame gimmick.
